{
  "texts": [
    "We found that prepending the source.",
    "term most significantly improved the performance of the model compared to the baseline input, but the combination of all parameters described above performed the best.",
    "Furthermore, we hypothesized that more context may lead to better performance and that context that comes before the ADE mention may have different value than context that comes after.",
    "We conducted experiments to examine whether the performance of the models would vary depending on the length of the input string that was extracted from the drug labels, or the proportion of the extracted string before and after the ADE term in question.",
    "We adjusted the length of the input string between 30 and 250 words, which was our maximum in using the language models."
  ]
}